    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously inspected and certified, this unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising mechanical and aesthetic quality. Experience a level of refinement that bridges the gap between pre-owned value and new-vehicle excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
